message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with speech processing and analysis. cs.CL is also likely as it deals with natural language processing and speech recognition. cs.LG is another possible category as it deals with machine learning techniques used in the paper. cs.SI is also possible as it deals with signal processing and analysis. cs.SY is less likely but still possible as it deals with control and systems engineering, which can be relevant to speech separation.
